quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"ql -ayha alrswl- liladhin kafaruu biallah wrswlh: ya 'ayuha alkafirun ballh"
  109,2,la 'aebud ma taebudun min al'asnam walalht alzayft
  109,3,"wla 'antum eabidun ma 'aebud min 'ilh wahd, hu allah rabu alealamin almsthq wahdah llebadt"
  109,4,wla 'ana eabid maa eabadtum min al'asnam walalht albatlt
  109,5,"wla 'antum eabidun mustaqbalaan ma aebd. whdhh alayat nazalat fi 'ashkhas baeyanhm min almshrkyn, qad ealim allah 'anahum la yuminun abdana"
  109,6,"lkm dinakum aldhy asrrtm ealaa atbaeh, waliun diniin aldhy la 'abghi ghyrh"
  110,1,"'idha tmm lak -ayha alrswl- alnasr ealaa kafaar qrysh, watama lak fath \"mkt"
  110,2,wrayt alkthyr min alnaas yadkhulun fi al'islam jamaeat jmaeat
  110,3,"'idha waqae dhlk fthya liliqa' rabik bal'ikthar min altsbyh bihamdih wal'ikthar min astghfarh, 'iinah kan twabana ealaa almusabihin walmstghfryn, yatub ealayhim wyrhmhm wyqbl twbthm"
  111,1,"khsrt yada 'abi lahab wshqy b'iydhayh rasul allah mhmda salaa allah ealayh wslm, waqad tuhaqiq khsran 'abi lhb"
  111,2,"ma aghna eanh maluh wwldh, falan yarudda eanh shyyana min eadhab allah 'iidha nazal bh"
  111,3,"sydkhl narana mtajjt, hu wamra'atuh alty kanat tahmil alshwk, fttrhh fi tariq alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm; ladhyath"
  111,4,"sydkhl narana mtajjt, hu wamra'atuh alty kanat tahmil alshwk, fttrhh fi tariq alnabiu salaa allah ealayh wslm; ladhyath"
  111,5,"fy enqha habl mhkm alfatl min lyf shadid khshn, turfae bih fi nar jhnm, thuma turma 'iilaa asflha"